      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "解一个方程，本质上是在问：什么样的x能让式子等于零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "把多项式画成一条曲线，方程的解就藏在图里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "曲线每一次穿过x轴的地方，就是一个实根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "cnt-1",
      "filename": "count-cnt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/count-cnt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "代数基本定理告诉我们，n次多项式在复数范围恰好有n个根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "cnt-2",
      "filename": "count-cnt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/count-cnt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "二次方程有两个根，三次有三个，四次有四个，一个都不多不少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "complex",
      "line_id": "cpx-2",
      "filename": "complex-cpx-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/complex-cpx-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.54,
      "size": 40608,
      "text": "如果曲线悬在轴上方或下方不肯相交，那对应的就是一对共轭复根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "numeric",
      "line_id": "num-2",
      "filename": "numeric-num-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/numeric-num-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "二分法盯住符号变化的区间，不断对半夹逼，把根越关越紧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "注意那些粉红色的根，如何随系数滑动、相遇甚至消失。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "summary",
